-hk/中國_(遊戲)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B_%28%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%29&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=e791e206\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/中國_(遊戲)</a>"},{"pid":"03ded9f183e596b3e9d17a38c7f16e172d600d6e","tid":2193361,"uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f517124d62db563cb097185200f5cf02659a7a","tid":2193361,"uid":250773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/amp/s/kknews.cc/game/33zm9no.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.au%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fgame%2F33zm9no.amp&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=7831bb85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.au/amp/s/kknews.cc/game/33zm9no.amp</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2bernjn/3o0s000078r6np7ps92n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2bernjn%2F3o0s000078r6np7ps92n.jpg&h=bc21f911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n版圖上帶上了台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f014fb27a34bebcab65f9ac58be983e4988e3fc4","tid":2193361,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6687a339c48a807a6cfe978b86e0b4fe0b158d4","tid":2193361,"uid":80104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bcbeeb1165d6d973138b11ee8a61a659dcfb7587","tid":2193361,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"即係唐朝simcity之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T19:26:22.000Z